The paper discusses the vulnerabilities of machine learning models to adversarial attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on explaining and exploring these vulnerabilities through visual analytics, which involves techniques from artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and information visualization (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.SI.
